data.description: LIVE OAK SCHOOLS--OAK HILLS SUBDIVISION--Great 3BR/2BA plus OFFICE/Study with 1863sf living in desirable Oak Hills Estates. This home has a clean and open split floor plan with kitchen overlooking dining and living area.  Master suite has a large garden tub, separate shower, large walk in closet with dual vanities and a water closet.  This home has a 20x20 covered patio with a large fenced backyard.  Roof replaced in 2022. Home has never flooded.  Flood zone x. Flood insurance is not required. No HOA.
